    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2002 Porsche 911 Carrera, a definitive analog driver\u2019s machine. This 996.2 features the refined 3.6L flat-six with VarioCam Plus, delivering 320hp through a precise G96 6-speed manual transaxle. Mechanically, this example is superlative: the IMS bearing has been proactively addressed with an LN Engineering retrofit, and a recent borescope inspection confirms pristine cylinder walls. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specs with zero bushing deflection, while the braking system utilizes four-piston monobloc calipers for immediate bite. The exterior retains its original deep luster, and the interior shows no bolster wear or UV degradation. A turn-key specimen for the technical purist.",
